title: The left wing is asking the wrong questions (vs. Vegan Commie John Sakars!)
description:
My earlier video discussing education policy (mentioned on-screen here) was, _The University is Broken: "Academically Adrift" Book Review._ Link = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J_KEXfDpeDs 
You don't want the link to John Sakars' channel do you?  DO YOU?  *Sigh.*  Fine, here it is: https://www.youtube.com/user/TheSakars/videos
The specific video I'm responding to here was titled, "Everything Should Be Free".  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l3nhg9B-aXk
Want to comment, ask questions and chat with other viewers?  Join the channel's Discord server (a discussion forum, better than a youtube comment section).  Click here: https://discord.gg/BsgnTm
Support the creation of new content on the channel (and speak to me, directly, if you want to) via Patreon, for $1 per month: https://www.patreon.com/a_bas_le_ciel
Find me on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/a_bas_le_ciel/?hl=en
Find me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/eiselmazard
You may not know that I have several youtube channels, one of them is AR&IO (Active Research & Informed Opinion) found here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCP3fLeOekX2yBegj9-XwDhA/videos
Another is à-bas-le-ciel, found here: https://www.youtube.com/user/HeiJinZhengZhi/videos
And there is, in fact, a youtube channel that has my own legal name, Eisel Mazard: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuxp5G-XFGcH4lmgejZddqA #vegans #veganism #politicsinpyjamas
